      <title>摩根大通高管说，马克龙“失去战斗”引诱PE。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/macron-lost-battle-for-private-equity-jpmorgan-executive-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）计划吸引更多私募股权公司加入巴黎的计划受到该国的政治动荡的阻碍，这是一名高级摩根大通（JPMorgan Chase＆amp＆amp;公司高管周四表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/macron-lost-battle-for-private-equity-jpmorgan-executive-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 14:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
